			{
				"id": "music:mixtapes-for-camille-1990",
				"slug": "mixtapes-for-camille-1990",
				"status": "published",
				"data": {
					"title": "Mixtapes for Camille: 1990",
					"featured_image": {
						"id": "",
						"provider": "external",
						"src": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/1990.jpg"
					},
					"content": [
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k1",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k0",
									"text": "For most of the past decade, our Wagstaff family tradition has been to run a single, simple gift exchange for Christmas. Instead of buying presents, we draw one family member's name and then make them a gift to be presented to them at next year's Christmas. It's been a great experience for everyone--we've all wasted less money buying things others didn't really need, we've learned all kinds of skills and handcrafts, and given and received beautiful, meaningful gifts to each other.",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k3",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k2",
									"text": "In 2010, I drew my youngest sister Camille, who loves to sing and who's often asked me for musical recommendations over the years. I decided that as part of her gift, I'd make a series of mixtapes, one for each year of her life (she was born in 1990). In addition to the normal mixtape rules (can't have 2 songs by the same artist, etc.) there was an additional constraint: the songs on each album had to have been released in the year in question. Making these was a blast and a real challenge, especially as I tried to offer a reflection of the range and variety of music released in that year. Below, I present the 1990 mix I made for Camille's Christmas gift. I'm sure I left some gems out, but I leave it for you to judge the quality of 1990's musical vintage.",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k5",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k4",
									"text": "Music-loving friends, if you were making this record, what else would you have included?",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k7",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k6",
									"text": "http://open.spotify.com/user/steelwagstaff/playlist/0RFXmBSO6c7u8OAuBaNXXO",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			},
			{
				"id": "music:mixtapes-camille-1991",
				"slug": "mixtapes-camille-1991",
				"status": "published",
				"data": {
