			{
				"id": "music:cedar-dance-parties-lullabies-round-3",
				"slug": "cedar-dance-parties-lullabies-round-3",
				"status": "published",
				"data": {
					"title": "Cedar Dance Parties &amp; Lullabies [Round 3]",
					"featured_image": {
						"id": "",
						"provider": "external",
						"src": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/IMG_4058.jpg"
					},
					"content": [
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k1",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k0",
									"text": "Our little man is almost a year old now (incredible!). We've continued our tradition of daily dance parties, and he's at the point where he can do a bit of shaking and jiving on his own, which is both hilarious and heartwarming. It's the best, really, having a tiny dancer in your family. My wife sent me a video this week as a goal for him to aspire to by age 2:",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k3",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k2",
									"text": "So that's what we're shooting for. With that in mind, here's the third set of Cedar Dance Parties & Lullabies (50 songs he grooved to in the past few weeks):",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k5",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k4",
									"text": "http://open.spotify.com/user/steelwagstaff/playlist/74ewy2HNWXvJXOPAEHpT59",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			},
			{
				"id": "music:mixtapes-for-laurel-bull",
				"slug": "mixtapes-for-laurel-bull",
				"status": "published",
				"data": {
					"title": "Mixtapes for Laurel: BULL",
					"featured_image": {
						"id": "",
						"provider": "external",
						"src": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/bull.jpg"
					},
					"content": [
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k1",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k0",
									"text": "When Laurel and I first began dating, we made each other a series of mixtapes--not the most original idea, but it was an important part of our getting to know each other. For me, I decided to make a series of four discs BULL WORK BIRD SONG that were both a play on Laurel's last name (Bastian = bastion = bulwark = BULL WORK) and presented a collection of connected, themed songs.",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k3",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k2",
									"text": "The first two discs (Bull and Work) featured only songs about animals (bulls, etc.) and the second two featured songs about birds and singing, respectively. Here's the first disc, BULL:",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "k5",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k4",
									"text": "http://open.spotify.com/user/steelwagstaff/playlist/0QYnKRuRIJFUQoCCIRKCi9",
									"marks": []
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "ku",
							"style": "normal",
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_key": "k6",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://media.sas.upenn.edu/pennsound/authors/Bunting/Bunting-Basil_Complete-Reading_SUNY-Buffalo_07-29-66.mp3"
								},
								{
									"_key": "k9",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8g0REgZYc_w"
								},
								{
									"_key": "kc",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KQ7z8gbb2i8"
								},
								{
									"_key": "kf",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XkGpo9RB0L4"
								},
								{
									"_key": "ki",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3K9_1R-bhF0"
								},
								{
									"_key": "kl",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WlOXX-SQjtM"
								},
								{
									"_key": "ko",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fYAZPynemNw"
								},
								{
									"_key": "kr",
									"_type": "link",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=375eARe1vNQ"
								}
							],
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k7",
									"text": "A few notes--the disc opened with a recording of Basil Bunting reading the first 40 seconds of his great poem [_Briggflatts_",
									"marks": [
										"k6"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k8",
									"text": ": \"Brag, sweet tenor bull ... \" and featured a number of tracks that aren't in Spotify's library: The Maccabees' \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "ka",
									"text": "Young Lions",
									"marks": [
										"k9"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kb",
									"text": "\", M. Doughty's \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kd",
									"text": "Frog and Banjo",
									"marks": [
										"kc"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "ke",
									"text": "\", Les Poppys' \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kg",
									"text": "Tous Les Animaux du Monde",
									"marks": [
										"kf"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kh",
									"text": "\", Bonnie 'Prince' Billy's \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kj",
									"text": "Little Boy Blue I",
									"marks": [
										"ki"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kk",
									"text": "\", Sufjan Stevens' \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "km",
									"text": "Wolverine",
									"marks": [
										"kl"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kn",
									"text": "\", Tom McRae's \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kp",
									"text": "Ghost of a Shark",
									"marks": [
										"ko"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "kq",
									"text": ",\" and Beck's \"",
									"marks": []
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "ks",
									"text": "Rosalie",
									"marks": [
										"kr"
									]
								},
								{
