								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-223-crvws",
									"text": "My favorite of these was Kleinzahler's book.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-224-cl30n",
									"text": "It's funny looking back at the list--I don't feel particularly impressed by the overall quality of my reading for the year, despite the volume. My big goal for 2018 is to finish and defend my dissertation, which means that I'll dedicate most of my reading energy to that for the first several months of the year. When it comes to leisure reading, my goal is to diminish my online news consumption even further and keep up the pace with books, particularly nonfiction--my goal is to read another 60 books in 2018.\n\n"
								},
