							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-221-97srd",
									"text": " Additional settings available in chapter editing menu[/caption]"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-224-06iqi",
							"style": "h4",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-223-b12nr",
									"text": "Producing Exports"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-228-s28gm",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-225-u0xxd",
									"text": "You probably noticed in our “landing page” example that visitors to the Portuguese textbook site could download a copy of the book for offline access in a number of different formats. That’s because Pressbooks also allows you to easily create exports of your book’s content and to download, publish, or share those exports in whatever way you like. In our case, the creators of our language textbook chose to publish the textbook under an open license, and wanted to make free (offline) copies of the book available to anyone who wants to learn Portuguese. Authors can produce exports of their content at any time from a ‘Export’ link available in the book’s dashboard.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-226-ctjnr",
									"text": "[caption id=\"attachment_6283\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"600\"]"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-227-8o621",
									"href": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.18.21-PM.png"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-229-rllj0",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.18.21-PM-600x267.png",
								"url": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.18.21-PM-600x267.png"
							},
							"alt": "pressbooks export page"
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-232-4zkt1",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-230-89pzm",
									"text": " Sample view of the export page for a Pressbook.[/caption]\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-231-tjqvc",
									"text": "This export page will generally include the following components:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-234-gmnju",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-233-j00jj",
									"text": "A big red ‘export your book’ button!"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-236-xm1q6",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-235-5kfvk",
									"text": "Several export format options (some of which require additional dependencies and additional installation, if you’re running your own Pressbooks network)"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-238-cdmtd",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-237-f3g3z",
									"text": "The last 5 batches of exported files you’ve made for a given book"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-246-dqusg",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-239-h1o7h",
									"text": "Information about the theme you’re using for your book. We’re using the excellent "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-241-tmpfp",
									"text": "Open Textbooks theme",
									"marks": [
										"key-240-zewpc"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-242-hpcew",
									"text": " for our book (with our deepest thanks to Brad Payne and the good folks at "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-244-xsngd",
									"text": "BCcampus",
									"marks": [
										"key-243-d7eki"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-245-2t3kx",
									"text": " for their work on and support for the Open Textbooks plugin)"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-240-zewpc",
									"href": "https://github.com/BCcampus/pressbooks-textbook",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-243-d7eki",
									"href": "https://bccampus.ca/staff-directory/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-249-cdjvr",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.26.35-PM-600x356.png",
								"url": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.26.35-PM-600x356.png"
							},
							"alt": ""
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-252-4001r",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-250-yf0os",
									"text": "If you want these exports to appear on the landing pages for individual books, you’ll need to enable this at the network level. Network administrators will see an option called ‘Sharing & Privacy’ in their network settings menu, and can select the ‘Allow book administrators to enable redistribution of export files’ option (pictured at right).\n\n"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-251-orkuv",
									"href": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.28.56-PM.png"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-253-gy6dh",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.28.56-PM-600x233.png",
								"url": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-09-at-1.28.56-PM-600x233.png"
							},
							"alt": ""
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-256-o9i6b",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-254-1geja",
									"text": "\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-255-4ngtg",
									"text": "If this setting is enabled, individual book authors will see a similar option available at the book level in their ‘Settings’-> ‘Sharing & Privacy’ menu under the title ‘Share Latest Export Files’ (shown below). If they select ‘yes’ to this option, the most recent exports for their book will be available for download on the book’s landing page."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-258-tzboh",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-257-h0l4f",
									"text": "Further Reading"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-261-7abl1",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-259-9ym4d",
									"text": "Phew! This has already gone on for quite some time, but I hope that it’s a helpful start. I realize that I’m not really even scratching the surface of some of the most interesting teaching & learning applications possible with open web publishing and a WordPress-based tool like Pressbooks, but I’ll have to leave that for another day. If you have any corrections, suggestions, or questions, I’d love to hear them.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-260-g3ij2",
									"text": "In the meantime, if you’re looking for further guides to using Pressbooks for open publishing projects connected to higher education, I’d recommend consulting (or contributing to!) the following resources:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-268-54ohi",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-262-mkgxz",
									"text": "This user guide written and maintained by Pressbooks: "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-264-8d36a",
									"text": "https://guide.pressbooks.com/",
									"marks": [
										"key-263-9xjgl"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-265-mmg2g",
									"text": " and these training videos: "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-267-oprso",
									"text": "https://www.youtube.com/user/pressbooks/videos",
									"marks": [
										"key-266-dczn8"
									]
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-263-9xjgl",
									"href": "https://guide.pressbooks.com/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-266-dczn8",
									"href": "https://www.youtube.com/user/pressbooks/videos",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-275-57b8p",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-269-oyswu",
									"text": "These two textbook authoring guides for Pressbooks: Lauri Aasoph and Amanda Coolidge’s original (published in 2014 by BCcampus): "
