								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-46-ltcy3",
									"text": ". I actually really liked my first exposure to the Aubrey & Maturin series. My friend Dave's been recommending these books to me for years, and I never took the plunge until I went to Chicago for a conference and had 5 hours in a hotel room next to the airport and a shopping mall. Reading was the best way I could have spent my time, and so I read "
