									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-29-amfsp",
									"text": "I also read Owen Davies' "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-30-fcvwl",
									"text": "Paganism: A Very Short Introduction",
									"marks": [
										"em"
