								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-157-oav35",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-156-ys6j2",
									"text": "Domain Registrar:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-165-s5yf1",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-158-bm91k",
									"text": "I’ve registered domain names with probably a dozen different companies over the years, some good, and some terrible. I have three criteria that matter to me: price, WHOIS privacy, and absence of upselling/marketing. I currently use NameSilo, which satisfies all three requirements for me. I’ve created "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-160-fyo22",
									"text": "an affiliate link",
									"marks": [
										"key-159-dntl8"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-161-og5qi",
									"text": " to allow anyone to get $1 off initial domain registrations (enter the coupon code ‘Medium’). Full disclosure: I will receive "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-163-17g4j",
									"text": "a 10% commission",
									"marks": [
										"key-162-mhodd"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-164-d56s1",
									"text": " for initial purchases from new accounts if you use my affiliate link."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-159-dntl8",
									"href": "https://www.namesilo.com/?rid=013ae26vx",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-162-mhodd",
									"href": "https://www.namesilo.com/account_affiliate_details.php",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-168-3ktox",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-166-9bxcl",
									"text": "Why I Like NameSilo: ",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-167-fvjt1",
									"text": "All they do is domain registration and they’ve never sent me unwanted solicitations or tried to upsell me anything. Very good prices for all kinds of TLDs and registering, renewing and transferring domains with them is quick and easy. They include WHOIS privacy in the purchase price. Finally, they have an affiliate program which lets me create $1 off coupons and earn a small commission on referrals (I don’t really care that much about this, but maybe you will)."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-170-dq15g",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-169-vnbco",
									"text": "2. Storage Space to Put Stuff: Web Hosting"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-172-6k52a",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-171-tuuj0",
									"text": "The second thing you need to have a website is space to store the material that people will see when they visit your domain. The most common solution to this is to rent space on someone else’s web server (a hard drive connected securely to the internet). Renting server space is commonly referred to as buying web ‘hosting.’ For a personal website, you will generally be just fine with what’s called a ‘shared hosting’ account, which means that your files will be stored on a server (hard drive) alongside the files of several other renters. Think of purchase shared web hosting as being like renting a storage unit — you all have units at the same property, but each of you has your own storage units with your own locks, so they can’t see and mess with your stuff, and you can’t see and mess with their stuff. There are all kinds of extra fancy things that web hosts offer (and will try to sell you), but most of them are unnecessary. You really only need space and bandwidth, and those generally are quite cheap."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-174-4g8lg",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-173-5zsel",
									"text": "My Hosting Recommendations:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-176-s98w5",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-175-v7qd6",
									"text": "For Personal Websites for Academics or Academic Organizations:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-184-dmlwq",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-177-5gma1",
									"text": "I strongly recommend buying hosting from "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-179-m34j7",
									"text": "Reclaim Hosting",
									"marks": [
										"key-178-12tlq"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-180-copuc",
									"text": ". They’re a small company founded in 2013 that grew out of the University of Mary Washington’s "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-182-3a0ll",
									"text": "A Domain of One’s Own",
									"marks": [
										"key-181-7ok58"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-183-loxdg",
									"text": " service, which was & is awesome, and not just because it paid homage to Virginia Woolf."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-178-12tlq",
									"href": "https://reclaimhosting.com/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-181-7ok58",
									"href": "https://reclaimhosting.com/domain-of-ones-own/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-193-lvk7y",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-185-m72m3",
									"text": "Why I like Reclaim:",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-186-n3hq3",
									"text": " their basic hosting services are fantastic, their customer service "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-188-8y5pa",
									"text": "is legendarily good",
									"marks": [
										"key-187-huczm"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-189-htg7h",
									"text": ", and their prices are unmatched. They offer three "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-191-luztt",
									"text": "shared hosting packages",
									"marks": [
										"key-190-smm8z"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-192-syx86",
									"text": ", which are identical, except for how much space they give you on the server. “Students & Individuals” gives you 2GB for $30/year, “Faculty & Professionals” gives you 10GB for $50/year and Large “Organizations” gives you 100GB for $100/year. If you’re just going to be hosting a simple personal website, 2GB should be more than enough space."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-187-huczm",
									"href": "https://reclaimhosting.com/what-people-are-saying/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-190-smm8z",
									"href": "https://reclaimhosting.com/shared-hosting/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-196-1bs2s",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-194-sr3r5",
									"text": "[caption id=\"attachment_6134\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1517\"]"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-195-gaytm",
									"href": "https://steelwagstaff.info/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Screen-Shot-2017-02-18-at-2.56.18-PM.png"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-197-r7h2v",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "http://localhost:4321/_emdash/api/media/file/01KNVY5KFR9HVB2YMSX2QADWA4.png",
								"url": "http://localhost:4321/_emdash/api/media/file/01KNVY5KFR9HVB2YMSX2QADWA4.png"
							},
							"alt": "Screenshot from Reclaim Hosting"
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-202-lgyaw",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-198-3d5zh",
									"text": " The three "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-200-2ur23",
									"text": "shared hosting packages",
									"marks": [
										"key-199-hqkqk"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-201-p13kx",
									"text": " offered by Reclaim Hosting.[/caption]"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-199-hqkqk",
									"href": "https://reclaimhosting.com/shared-hosting/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-204-xkrpj",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-203-8jcpv",
									"text": "Hosting for Registered Nonprofit Organizations:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-215-edz33",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-205-dmir5",
									"text": "If you work for a registered nonprofit organization, I’d recommend applying for "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-207-07vy0",
									"text": "Dreamhost’s free shared hosting account",
									"marks": [
										"key-206-8hld8"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-208-gq50f",
									"text": ". You have to provide documentation that you’re a registered 501(c)3 organization, but if you provide that, you’re eligible for a single shared hosting account, which should do everything you need to host a simple organizational website. I’ve helped a handful of nonprofits use this service, and have been impressed with Dreamhost’s hosting and customer support (and the price is literally unbeatable!). Registered non-profits can also get free or heavily discounted access to a number of other great technology tools, like "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-210-g8et4",
									"text": "Slack",
									"marks": [
										"key-209-fq0jd"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-211-ecrcu",
									"text": " and "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-213-lc3wh",
									"text": "Airtable",
									"marks": [
										"key-212-btv55"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-214-7zzjc",
									"text": ", to name just two."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-206-8hld8",
									"href": "https://help.dreamhost.com/hc/en-us/articles/215769478-Non-profit-discount",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-209-fq0jd",
									"href": "https://get.slack.help/hc/en-us/articles/204368833-Slack-for-Nonprofits",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-212-btv55",
									"href": "https://airtable.com/shr9DxhP6lU9slZE6",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-217-8cdt6",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-216-twtmx",
									"text": "If you need something bigger/better:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-225-ky9dh",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-218-2u71k",
									"text": "I’ve had good shared hosting experiences with both Bluehost and Dreamhost. I currently have a Bluehost Plus account ("
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-220-2g486",
									"text": "introductory price",
									"marks": [
										"key-219-p4pq1"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-221-1iaka",
									"text": "$5.45/mo for 36 months, following which the standard price is $10.99/mo). Dreamhost’s "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-223-nnu90",
									"text": "base price is $10.95 / month",
									"marks": [
										"key-222-viug1"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-224-wmbnh",
									"text": ", but discounts kick in if you sign up for a longer duration up front. If you buy 3 years of hosting upfront, your monthly cost will be just $7.95/mo, for example, and if you buy 10 years, the monthly price drops to $5.95/mo. If I needed more server space than Reclaim offered and wanted to set up a shared hosting account right now, I’d choose bluehost if I thought the site would only exist for 3 years or less, and Dreamhost if I envisioned it being around for longer."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-219-p4pq1",
									"href": "https://my.bluehost.com/cgi/help/price",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-222-viug1",
									"href": "https://help.dreamhost.com/hc/en-us/articles/215560437-What-types-of-hosting-plans-are-available-",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-227-avyy0",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-226-wkauw",
									"text": "3. A method for writing, publishing, and editing your content: Content Management System"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-235-62mtz",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-228-03avy",
									"text": "Once you’ve got a domain [an address] and web hosting [space to put stuff], the last thing you’ll need is a system for writing, editing and publishing the content you want to appear at your domain. You can (and maybe should!) "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-230-oywr0",
									"text": "learn to write HTML5, CSS3, and javascript yourself",
									"marks": [
										"key-229-y14qy"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-231-33qhl",
									"text": " and hand code your site (that’s where I got my start and how I built my first several sites), but most you probably have other places where you’d like to spend your time. Fortunately, there are a number of Content Management Systems [CMSes] which you can use to produce and display dynamic web content. The three most commonly used CMSes on the web today are WordPress [58.7% of sites that use a CMS, according to "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-233-feeex",
									"text": "February 2017 data from W3Techs",
									"marks": [
										"key-232-rzuh9"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-234-9y2n6",
									"text": "], Joomla [7.1%], and Drupal [4.7%]. Each is free and open source software, and all can be used to build beautiful websites."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-229-y14qy",
									"href": "https://dash.generalassemb.ly/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-232-rzuh9",
									"href": "https://w3techs.com/technologies/history_overview/content_management",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-237-jzo68",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-236-yilt9",
									"text": "You can also use all-in-one website builder tools which bundle design with domain registration and hosting from companies like Squarespace, Wix, or Weebly. Many users find these tools easy to use and they let people build attractive, template-based sites for a reasonable fee (they’re usually not much more expensive than typical shared hosting accounts). Downsides are that they are more expensive that using a self-hosted open-source CMS (free!) and that it can be very difficult to get your content out once you’ve put it in, which means that you’re essentially locking yourself in to being a long-term customer of the company. If they raise their rates, you’re often pretty much stuck, unless you want to rebuild your site somewhere else. For these reasons, I recommend installing an open-source CMS on your own self-hosted site."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-239-haznw",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-238-nhdoh",
									"text": "My CMS Recommendation:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-253-dg9l7",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-240-4sdxd",
									"text": "For almost everyone who is new to web development and wants to build a basic information site (with the ability to blog), I’d recommend using WordPress, which you can "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-242-bw1du",
									"text": "download from their website",
									"marks": [
										"key-241-ojskn"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-243-2w7w4",
									"text": " and install in just a few minutes ("
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-245-xh1yt",
									"text": "they promise a 5-minute install",
									"marks": [
										"key-244-76cyq"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-246-cp6cz",
									"text": ", but that may be a little optimistic for most first time users). Many people are already familiar with WordPress through wordpress.com, which is a commercial software-as-a-service instance of WordPress where users can build basic free websites and let someone else handle hosting and server configuration. After I became curious about CMSes after a few years of building my own websites with pure HTML/CSS, I started on the .com version of "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-248-teeto",
									"text": "WordPress",
									"marks": [
										"key-247-bmrgh"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-249-rtuxi",
									"text": " before eventually moving on to the WordPress-powered self-hosted site that I now maintain at "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-251-4jzpz",
									"text": "http://steelwagstaff.info",
									"marks": [
										"key-250-i9ofv"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-252-uc5ei",
									"text": ". Wordress.com is certainly a nice gateway for new website builders, but going the self-hosted WordPress.org route provides you with lots more flexibility and no additional costs (apart from hosting and domain registration). Here’s a quick comparison of the two methods:"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-241-ojskn",
									"href": "https://wordpress.org/download/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-244-76cyq",
									"href": "https://codex.wordpress.org/Installing_WordPress",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-247-bmrgh",
									"href": "https://steelwagstaff.wordpress.com/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-250-i9ofv",
									"href": "http://steelwagstaff.info./",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-255-jgf19",
							"style": "h4",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-254-xa90e",
									"text": "WordPress.com"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-257-xxecg",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-256-zzuh3",
									"text": "You go to wordpress.com, register an available second-level domain (EXAMPLE.wordpress.com) and build your website. Wordpress.com is actually a big multisite network administered by someone else, so you’re constrained in what you can install and change. They have a bunch of already installed and configured tools and plugins that you can use to make your site look the way you want it to, but if you want to move beyond the fairly narrow range of themes and configuration options, you’ll have to begin paying for a premium account, and some things just aren’t permitted or allowed because of how the multisite is configured."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-260-93nvt",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-258-4tfwc",
									"text": "Pros:",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-259-648aw",
									"text": " Someone else handles hosting and server configuration. You can make a free site quickly and beautifully with easy to use tools, provided you don’t mind having a .wordpress.com domain and can live within the constraints of the free plan."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-263-sduf0",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-261-jqce3",
									"text": "Cons:",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-262-kadvw",
									"text": " Your domain has to end with wordpress.com (doesn’t always convey the right professional image). If you want to do more than a few basic customizations, you have to start paying."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-265-fm9l6",
							"style": "h4",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-264-5va2x",
									"text": "WordPress.org"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-267-90fb4",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-266-n8q38",
									"text": "You download the WordPress software and install on your web host. Once you’ve set up your database and configured the installation, you can then create content, select a theme, and install and configure plugins. The range of possibilities with WordPress is quite vast."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-270-35hge",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-268-dfqp1",
									"text": "Pros: ",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-269-rdacz",
									"text": "This is free, open-source software, so you only have to pay for hosting (unless you want to buy premium themes or plugins). Plugins exist for almost anything you can imagine. You can make your site look however you want, almost. You can make all kinds of decisions and do things yourself!"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-273-nxgsb",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-271-e0pxp",
									"text": "Cons: ",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-272-qbknu",
									"text": "You have to make decisions and do things yourself."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-285-xklbl",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-274-r3tgy",
									"text": "Note for friends: ",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-275-kqntt",
									"text": "If you decide you want to go the self-hosted WordPress route, I purchased the "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-277-jikoc",
									"text": "ProPlus package",
									"marks": [
										"key-276-yjb64"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-278-4etmt",
									"text": " from StudioPress a few years back, which means that I have the ability to install the Genesis Framework and any of their child themes on as many sites as I want for the rest of time. The "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-280-qoj9m",
									"text": "Genesis framework",
									"marks": [
										"key-279-bbz3w"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-281-eydt9",
									"text": " is really nice, and "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-283-b8kdf",
									"text": "their themes",
									"marks": [
										"key-282-qkk6i"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-284-dv3f2",
									"text": " are generally quite good. If one of those looks good to you and you want to use it — let me know, and I’ll happily help you out."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-276-yjb64",
									"href": "http://my.studiopress.com/pro-plus/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-279-bbz3w",
									"href": "http://my.studiopress.com/themes/genesis/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-282-qkk6i",
									"href": "http://my.studiopress.com/themes/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-287-3igqp",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-286-ppgx1",
									"text": "Postscript: Learning More about Web Development"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-289-45ndh",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-288-o078t",
									"text": "Want to learn more about HTML/CSS + Javascript?"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-300-t7t0r",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-290-z6qjv",
									"text": "Try "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-292-ldpl3",
									"text": "Dash",
									"marks": [
										"key-291-jtwi0"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-293-ksxp1",
									"text": ", a browser-based learning tool from General Assembly. "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-295-1v2ut",
									"text": "Lynda.com",
									"marks": [
										"key-294-hnxyg"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-296-iu71j",
									"text": "has a number of great video tutorials which may be free to you (if your institution provides a subscription — my university provides students and faculty with access through their NetIDs), or you may want to try a freemium service like "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-298-8e09t",
									"text": "Codecademy",
									"marks": [
										"key-297-eprvk"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-299-j7fdg",
									"text": "."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-291-jtwi0",
									"href": "https://dash.generalassemb.ly/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-294-hnxyg",
									"href": "https://kb.wisc.edu/page.php?id=21984",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-297-eprvk",
									"href": "https://www.codecademy.com/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-302-g536q",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-301-h9mhp",
									"text": "Want to learn more about advanced features and general design?"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-325-365p0",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-303-lsh4l",
									"text": "You’ll probably want to know about "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-305-kigt1",
									"text": "Stack Overflow",
									"marks": [
										"key-304-xyyu9"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-306-l3j2f",
									"text": ", an enormous online forum where questions about programming are asked and answered. I’d also recommend "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-308-0fb2c",
									"text": "Smashing Magazine",
									"marks": [
										"key-307-aeea4"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-309-50vlo",
									"text": ", Jeffrey Zeldman’s "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-311-th7ve",
									"text": "A List Apart",
									"marks": [
										"key-310-4hej6"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-312-rgye7",
									"text": ", and "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-314-kjrfp",
									"text": "Codrops",
									"marks": [
										"key-313-ijtv3"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-315-7bd57",
									"text": ". If you care about beautiful web typography, check out "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-317-x3149",
									"text": "Typewolf",
									"marks": [
										"key-316-mw0c2"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-318-qruev",
									"text": ", "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-320-0rfa9",
									"text": "Typeconnection",
									"marks": [
										"key-319-cpk9g"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-321-gs17k",
									"text": ", and "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-323-u86lz",
									"text": "The Elements of Typographic Style Applied to the Web",
									"marks": [
										"key-322-3o0x2"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-324-0ejf0",
									"text": "for some good ideas and starting points."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-304-xyyu9",
									"href": "http://stackoverflow.com/tags",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-307-aeea4",
									"href": "https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2008/01/10-principles-of-effective-web-design/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-310-4hej6",
									"href": "http://alistapart.com/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-313-ijtv3",
									"href": "http://tympanus.net/codrops/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-316-mw0c2",
									"href": "https://www.typewolf.com/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-319-cpk9g",
									"href": "http://www.typeconnection.com/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-322-3o0x2",
									"href": "http://webtypography.net/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-333-7jduf",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-326-ztpcz",
									"text": "Strange as it sounds, books on graphic & web design and on programming languages [HTML5, CSS, Javascript, and PHP are the most important for web publishing] are a good idea. If you want digital books, your university or local public library likely offers access to at least some useful eBook collections. My employer, for example, provides students and staff with access to several large "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-328-7adyl",
									"text": "eBook collections",
									"marks": [
										"key-327-xyvzc"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-329-achvl",
									"text": ", one of which, "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-331-sxuzm",
									"text": "Safari Books Online",
									"marks": [
										"key-330-036t5"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-332-cyxy9",
									"text": ", contains most titles published by O’Reilly Books, a leading technology publisher."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-327-xyvzc",
									"href": "https://databases.library.wisc.edu/browse/e-book-collections",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-330-036t5",
									"href": "https://search.library.wisc.edu/database/UWI12534",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-335-vi0lm",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-334-v4aoi",
									"text": "Want to take a course in web design/development?"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-346-a33q3",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-336-53p2j",
									"text": "On my campus, the best place for this is in our School of Library and Information Studies [newly rebranded as the "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-338-sel8u",
									"text": "iSchool",
									"marks": [
										"key-337-kpj41"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-339-c0hoe",
									"text": "]. If you’re in or near Madison, one of my heroines, "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-341-vz0r4",
									"text": "Dorothea Salo",
									"marks": [
										"key-340-yj530"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-342-93gwq",
									"text": ", regularly teaches a "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-344-wiotv",
									"text": "Code and Power course",
									"marks": [
										"key-343-ks9ls"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-345-1rb7f",
									"text": " [LIS 640] which offers a good introduction to HTML/CSS code (and a lot more)."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-337-kpj41",
									"href": "https://slis.wisc.edu/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-340-yj530",
									"href": "http://dsalo.info/",
									"blank": true
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-343-ks9ls",
									"href": "http://dsalo.info/pdfs/uploads/2016/01/640CodePowersyll2015.pdf",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-362-qkbjh",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-347-i9on2",
									"text": "Online, there are LOTS of short, self-paced free & open courses available: see lists "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-349-1tisu",
									"text": "here",
									"marks": [
										"key-348-xbs3b"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-350-9vmn5",
									"text": " [MOOC List], "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
