			{
				"id": "posts:my-december-2016-reading",
				"slug": "my-december-2016-reading",
				"status": "published",
				"data": {
					"title": "My December 2016 Reading",
					"content": [
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-2-pddey",
							"style": "h2",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-1-3oi3v",
									"text": "Books"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-4-pq31i",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-3-3lekh",
									"text": "As the year limped its way to a close, I tried to keep up my torrid reading pace. I slowed down considerably from my October/November frenzy, and spent a lot more of my free time reading and writing on dissertation related topics (hi, Objectivist poets!) but still managed to read a fair number of interesting books in December. Here are some of them:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-6-dds5e",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-5-678sm",
									"text": "Poetry"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-13-x3gvz",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-7-q39e3",
									"text": "Robert Lax's "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-9-whbgj",
									"text": "Love Had a Compass: Journals and Poetry",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-8-zvil2"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-10-825d5",
									"text": ". Includes "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-11-9q4fa",
									"text": "The Circus of the Sun",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-12-9j9p7",
									"text": ", probably his best-regarded single volume. Here's a small taste of the poetry in that book:"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-8-zvil2",
									"href": "http://www.groveatlantic.com/?title=Love+Had+a+Compass",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-28-qan16",
							"style": "blockquote",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-14-t80z9",
									"text": "After supper light on fields, prairie, long yellow\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-15-i77yv",
									"text": "light on fields aspiring, fields looking up grass singing\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-16-i52id",
									"text": "high grass singing yellow light on green grass growing,\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-17-c9u9b",
									"text": "the wide round horizon, the long tired light on the field\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-18-j8nuy",
									"text": "and the green grass high yearning up aspiring to heaven\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-19-5x2b1",
									"text": "to the dome sky heaven the grass growing up to the sky\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-20-1w4jp",
									"text": "and the light dying, the sun wearily sleepily smiling\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-21-v031l",
									"text": "lying down, with a sighing song, a long smiling sigh\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-22-7kdhx",
									"text": "over the fields and the grass rising, thin prayer rising\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-23-7vwpc",
									"text": "tufted to the air above the field to the sky the dome\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-24-h9mb4",
									"text": "sky thin made of light air the dome above the field and\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-25-c59mz",
									"text": "the field breathing the air full rich golden grass smelling\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-26-7u40s",
									"text": "sweet and tired with sun dying sun lying down, dying down\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-27-qo2fb",
									"text": "in west."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-30-y7dxh",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-29-wo58e",
									"text": "Fiction"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-37-mz1yv",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-31-5o36k",
									"text": "I finally finished Ignazio Silone's "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-33-qbhg1",
									"text": "Abruzzo trilogy",
									"marks": [
										"key-32-vncg9"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-34-lx7xd",
									"text": " after stalling out halfway through "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-35-5n1il",
									"text": "The Seed Beneath the Snow ",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-36-a9c79",
									"text": "several months ago. Glad I finished the books, and glad to have read them, though I'm not exactly sure who'd I recommend them to."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-32-vncg9",
									"href": "https://www.amazon.com/Abruzzo-Trilogy-Fontamara-Bread-Beneath/dp/1586420062",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-42-08ab6",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-38-r7e88",
									"text": "David Foenikos' "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-40-lfdss",
									"text": "The Erotic Potential of My Wife",
									"marks": [
										"key-39-gw5ad",
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-41-rmwqp",
									"text": ". Quick, absurd, and very, very funny. Came highly recommended by a French-speaking Polish language professor here. Thanks Ewa!"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-39-gw5ad",
									"href": "http://www.saqibooks.co.uk/book/erotic-potential-wife/",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-44-71wk1",
							"style": "h3",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-43-98l0w",
									"text": "Non-fiction"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-46-nktp9",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-45-2lytm",
									"text": "I read a half-dozen 'very short introductions' and continued muddling my way slowly through several longer books. The VSI's I read in December were:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-51-bunyo",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-47-pe9c7",
									"text": "L. Sandy Maisel's "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-49-90c3y",
									"text": "American Political Parties and Elections",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-48-kvfch"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-50-0etcf",
									"text": ".",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-48-kvfch",
									"href": "https://global.oup.com/academic/product/american-political-parties-and-elections-a-very-short-introduction-9780195301229?cc=us&lang=en&",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-56-wtzhs",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "number",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-52-f80ea",
									"text": "Timothy Lim's "
