							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-85-z2yrw",
									"text": "I'm still plowing my way slowly through a few other nonfiction books: Mary Beard’s "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-87-77x23",
									"text": "SPQR: A History of Ancient Rome",
