								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-31-zrytb",
									"text": "effective altruism",
									"marks": [
										"key-30-5slf9"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-32-wzc4t",
									"text": ", a new trend in charitable giving, and some of the principles of ethical utilitarianism. Laurel and I have been guided in our thinking about chartiable giving by "
