						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-59-57il6",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-31-6qwwz",
									"text": "[/caption]\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-32-8k5d7",
									"text": "While we were in Crandon listening to presentations by Tina Van Zile, "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-34-c8pb0",
									"text": "Glenn Reynolds",
									"marks": [
										"key-33-9iitl"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-35-88ys4",
									"text": " (the tribe's legal counsel), and "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-37-lotmw",
									"text": "Roman Ferdinand",
									"marks": [
										"key-36-f5h1x"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-38-cba1o",
									"text": " (the tribe's hydrogeologist), we were pleasantly surprised by the arrival of members of the "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-40-szyl1",
									"text": "Bad River Chippewa band",
									"marks": [
										"key-39-mmqyt"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-41-pnida",
									"text": ", including a tribal elder and Mike Wiggins Jr., the band's current chairman--an event which was not on our scheduled itinerary. Chairman Wiggins and his colleagues had come to Crandon because they wanted to discuss strategy regarding their ongoing battle to stop "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-43-9eblx",
									"text": "Gogebic Taconite's plans",
									"marks": [
										"key-42-0woqa"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-44-4788x",
									"text": " to open an open pit iron ore mine in an area between Anderson in Iron County and Morse in Ashland County, "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-46-yqe92",
									"text": "a plan",
									"marks": [
										"key-45-a4u8p"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-47-e3nt1",
									"text": " which Chairman Wiggins fears will prove disastrous for his people, "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-49-06npd",
									"text": "their way of life",
									"marks": [
										"key-48-5b7p8"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-50-55gsp",
									"text": ", and "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-52-j4rtb",
									"text": "the quality of their environment",
									"marks": [
										"key-51-883ug"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-53-68fwe",
									"text": ". Borrowing from a strategy which proved to be key in the Sakaogan band's efforts to block the Crandon mine permits, in July of 2009, the Bad River band recently succeeded in completing"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-55-xlydy",
									"text": "a Water Quality Standards program application",
									"marks": [
										"key-54-fw6lc"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-56-k22no",
									"text": ", under which the EPA granted the band authority to run its own water quality standards program on its reservation. In his remarks to us, Chairman Wiggins indicated that the band was nearing completion of these standards and hoped to have them finalized and approved before the DNR makes a decision on Gocebic Taconite's impending application for a mining permit.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-57-1d0lj",
									"text": "[caption id=\"attachment_294\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"500\" caption=\"Mike Wiggins, Jr., Chairman of the Bad River Band of Lake Superior Chippewa Indians\"]"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-33-9iitl",
									"href": "http://www.reynlaw.net/contact.html"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-36-f5h1x",
									"href": "http://www.wi.nrcs.usda.gov/partnerships/tcacmembers.html"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-39-mmqyt",
									"href": "http://www.badriver-nsn.gov/history"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-42-0woqa",
									"href": "http://www.gogebictaconite.com/"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-45-a4u8p",
