								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-48-5b7p8",
									"href": "http://www.nature.org/ourinitiatives/regions/northamerica/unitedstates/wisconsin/the-nature-conservancy-in-wisconsin-protecting-the-place-where-food-grows.xml"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-51-883ug",
									"href": "http://nativetimes.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=5221:chippewa-tribal-leader-warns-lawmakers-on-mining-plans&catid=56&Itemid=32"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-54-fw6lc",
									"href": "http://www.epa.gov/r5water/wqs5/wqstribes.htm"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-58-d3jd8",
									"href": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/05/chairman_wiggins.jpg"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-60-l9azu",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/05/chairman_wiggins.jpg",
								"url": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/05/chairman_wiggins.jpg"
							},
							"alt": "photograph of Mike Wiggins, Jr."
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-100-oibg0",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-61-6f4qd",
									"text": "[/caption]\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-62-e38it",
									"text": "Chairman Wiggins also informed us of a distressing proposal to alter the licensing procedure for iron mines in the state. The full draft of this bill (along with a 20+ page Analysis by the nonpartisan Legislative Review Bureau) can be found "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-64-rq31j",
									"text": "here",
									"marks": [
										"key-63-nj32l"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-65-v0kjv",
									"text": "--if you care about mining and environmental issues in Wisconsin--I'd highly recommend reading the at least the overview. "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-67-o7krx",
									"text": "Clean Wisconsin",
									"marks": [
										"key-66-zvjng"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-68-i5iw1",
									"text": ", the state's oldest and largest environmental protection group, has also published their own "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-70-8p3y7",
									"text": "summary of the proposed legislation",
									"marks": [
										"key-69-44row"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-71-1lq5m",
									"text": ".\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-72-88y7g",
									"text": "I'm deeply concerned about these proposals--mining does produce great wealth, and human demand for resources is massive (and growing), but the environmental and health costs of the extraction industry are enormous (read documentary poet Mark Nowak's excellent book "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-74-8akcb",
									"text": "Coal Mountain Elementary",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-73-fchuv"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-75-mkckt",
									"text": " and subscribe to his "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-77-rjfvj",
									"text": "Coal Mountain",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-76-ss4oe"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-78-kzdfv",
									"text": " ",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-79-t13ed",
									"text": "blog for daily reminders of the cost of the global coal extraction industry), and their concentrated devastation and destruction seems to my mind in many cases to override the potential benefits that these proposed mines would offer.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-80-4g0kr",
									"text": "For more information about this specific proposal, here are a few sources of information:\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-81-e8lzf",
									"text": "This enthusiastic November 2010 Milwaukee Journal-Sentinel "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-83-4jnsg",
									"text": "article",
									"marks": [
										"key-82-fbyi1"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-84-lakw3",
									"text": " (which focuses on the anticipated financial benefits and job creation from the proposed mine). The article contains a lot of good information, but ends with this quote from a Iron County board member (and ex-mine worker): \"The county is 100% in support of this\"--so you can judge for yourself about the article's overall accuracy.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-85-t4wzb",
									"text": "This "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-87-fa47l",
									"text": "critical article",
									"marks": [
										"key-86-zijyt"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-88-u3owb",
									"text": " in the Chippewa Valley Post about the Gogebic Taconite mine and the draft of the mining legislation.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-89-ob6xb",
									"text": "This "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-91-r7x4c",
									"text": "resource-rich page",
									"marks": [
										"key-90-polev"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-92-7y2vm",
									"text": " from the Nature Conservancy about mining in the Penokee Range.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-93-puhhd",
									"text": "A "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-95-25991",
									"text": "short transcript",
									"marks": [
										"key-94-3q67n"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-96-vwcc3",
									"text": " of a piece produced for Wisconsin Public Radio on the environmental impacts of the proposed mine.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-97-j3eff",
									"text": "So, what to do about this? Inform yourself and then take action. After requesting and analyzing information on this proposal, stand up, speak out, support those who are fighting the proposal, and do some fighting yourself.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-98-pzo99",
									"text": "Here are a few ideas:\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-99-l59ah",
									"text": "On their website, Gogebic Taconite writes that they"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-63-nj32l",
									"href": "http://www.scribd.com/doc/55226562/Mining-Bill"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-66-zvjng",
									"href": "http://www.cleanwisconsin.org/index.php?module=cms&page=5"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-69-44row",
									"href": "http://cleanwisconsin.org/proxy.php?filename=files%2FMining+law+summary.pdf"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-73-fchuv",
									"href": "http://www.amazon.com/Coal-Mountain-Elementary-Mark-Nowak/dp/1566892287"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-76-ss4oe",
									"href": "http://coalmountain.wordpress.com/"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-82-fbyi1",
									"href": "http://www.jsonline.com/news/wisconsin/108584724.html"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-86-zijyt",
									"href": "http://chippewavalleypost.com/?p=2537"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-90-polev",
									"href": "http://www.nature.org/ourinitiatives/regions/northamerica/unitedstates/wisconsin/mining-in-the-penokee-gogebic-range-whats-at-risk.xml"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-94-3q67n",
									"href": "http://www.businessnorth.com/kuws.asp?RID=3732"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-105-afj2r",
							"style": "blockquote",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-101-uefty",
									"text": "have spent the last couple of months getting to know many of our neighbors and listening to the questions raised about how we would design, engineer, permit, construct and operate the GTAC iron ore mine in a responsible manner. These discussions and our interaction with all our neighbors have been very important to us and we hope to continue these dialogues as we move forward through the permitting process. If you have questions you would like us to address, or have a community project you believe we should support, please feel free to contact us at "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-103-y79x6",
									"text": "info@gogebictaconite.com",
									"marks": [
										"key-102-vagsb"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-104-m5lk7",
									"text": "."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-102-vagsb",
									"href": "https://mail.google.com/mail?view=cm&tf=0&to=info@gogebictaconite.com",
									"blank": true
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-139-wfuoy",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-106-o17ez",
									"text": "Write Gogebic Taconite with direct questions, or even suggest supporting the Bad River band's community project (stop the mine from receiving a permit--ha!).\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-107-nksby",
									"text": "Contact your "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-109-g040o",
									"text": "State Legislators",
									"marks": [
										"key-108-2ge48"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-110-3zd42",
									"text": " and let them know your feelings about the draft of the Ferrous Metallic Mining law (LRB‐2035/1) you've read and find our their position. Encourage them to update their position to reflect your views.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-111-uo1qk",
									"text": "Contact "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-113-x4usx",
									"text": "Ervin Soulier",
									"marks": [
										"key-112-czwfv"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-114-ixdru",
									"text": ", the Bad River Band's Natural Resources Manager, to see what you can do to help the Bad River band protect the quality of their environment. Consult "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-116-gjevu",
									"text": "this list",
									"marks": [
										"key-115-dwncf"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-117-qqu0j",
									"text": " to find other relevant members of the Wisconsin Tribal Conservation Advisory Council Members if you're interested in reaching further afield.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-118-ythob",
									"text": "Join the ongoing "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-120-n08na",
									"text": "Mother Earth Water Walk",
									"marks": [
										"key-119-fu0vv"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-121-kst3e",
									"text": ", in which Anishinaabe women walking from the four cardinal directions of the North American continent will converge on Bad River, Wisconsin on the weekend of June 11-13. Suggestions for involvement can be found on the last page of "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-123-shql0",
									"text": "this brochure",
									"marks": [
										"key-122-1c0d0"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-124-wln1k",
									"text": " and more information is contained in this "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-126-u36cw",
									"text": "press release",
									"marks": [
										"key-125-v3nzu"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-127-jiyx1",
									"text": ". Special thanks to Diana Peterson for the link to the website.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-129-t22dg",
									"text": "Write a letter",
									"marks": [
										"key-128-9lc37"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-130-pdzjg",
									"text": " to your local newspaper or community newsletter about this legislation or the Gogebic Taconite proposal and how it will likely affect the nearby Native American community. If you want to start small, I edit the Eagle Heights newsletter, a small monthly newsletter for the "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-132-8t7uf",
									"text": "University Apartments community",
									"marks": [
										"key-131-arhj8"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-133-53167",
									"text": " at UW-Madison (circulation: 1250) and would welcome a brief editorial/information piece/personal narrative from anyone who'd like to produce such a piece on this or any other environmental issue of local concern.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-134-1fydk",
									"text": "Join Clean Wisconsin's "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-136-jnczb",
									"text": "Action Network",
									"marks": [
										"key-135-bbmy5"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-137-ngtx0",
									"text": " to join their efforts to preserve Wisconsin's environment.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-138-2tqey",
									"text": "Any other information or suggestions would be greatly appreciated."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
