									"text": " by JULIA IOFFE",
									"marks": [
										"strong",
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-61-h3kuk",
									"text": "The first time I interviewed Ezra Klein, the 28-year-old prince of D.C. media, he brought me a sandwich: prosciutto on a poppy-seed baguette. (Also, chips and a beverage.",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
