								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-204-e5ms9",
									"text": "Kathy Martin (9) competing in the 3,000 meters in January at the Armory in Manhattan.    The crowd, small but noisy, fixed eyes on Kathy Martin, the woman in last place. Early on, she was fifth in a pack of 11 runners, calmly moving in heavy traffic.",
