								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-214-zy8d0",
									"text": "I’m not Dutch but, in 1976, my family moved to the Netherlands. Though my new classmates were only seven, most cycled to school alone. Later our town got “coffee shops” that sold dope legally.",
