									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-219-crpp5",
									"text": "Dozens of Nepalese migrant labourers have died in Qatar in recent weeks and thousands more are enduring appalling labour abuses, a Guardian investigation has found, raising serious questions about Qatar's preparations to host the 2022 World Cup.",
