							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-121-xlf59",
									"text": "Every day a piece of computer code is sent to me by e-mail from a website to which I subscribe called IFTTT. Those letters stand for the phrase “if this then that,” and the code is in the form of a “recipe” that has the power to animate it."
								}
