							"style": "blockquote",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-135-zanq5",
									"text": "The Black-Scholes equation was the mathematical justification for the trading that plunged the world's banks into catastrophe It was the holy grail of investors."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-140-jte3i",
