							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-155-pueta",
									"text": "The furor over analytics (re-)sparked by Charles Barkley’s pre-All-Star Week tirade has gotten us here at Nylon Calculus talking. Moving past the immediate, defensive reactions to Barkley’s particular perspective1, there was something to be taken from the discussion."
								}
