							"style": "blockquote",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-169-n15rs",
									"text": "Marrakech, 2001 or 2002, maybe, and Errol Morris wants camels. Real, spontaneous camels — the kind you see wandering across the desert in children’s books. In his documentaries, Morris is known for staging and re-creation, for artifice."
								}
