				"data": {
					"title": "Whittenberger Update",
					"content": [
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-3-748f9",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-1-hx9q9",
									"text": "I wrote several months ago about my efforts to reconnect with several of my fellow 1998 Whittenberger Summer Writing Project attendees. Since then, the Facebook group has swelled to nearly half a dozen, and I'd say the successfuly contact rate is around 65%. Here's an update:\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-2-ubpew",
									"text": "Here's the full list of the 1998 Whittenberger Summer Writing Project Attendees. Names in bold are current members of the private Facebook group I created to contact fellow attendees:"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-7-1k0xv",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "bullet",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-4-aklg2",
									"text": "Joy Barbour",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-5-9zn9j",
									"text": " (Boise): Earned degree in journalism from "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-6-lisf8",
									"text": "University of Idaho to earn my journalism degree. Married in 2004 and started working for Idaho Press-Tribune in Nampa. I was the editor of a couple of their magazines for four years. Became a mother in 2008. Now has a son and daughter. Still in Treasure Valley area and still loves words!"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-10-bhlam",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "bullet",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-8-p84b9",
									"text": "Jessica Barrow",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-9-nkl7t",
									"text": " (Eagle): Now Jess Westhoff. American Studies major at University of Idaho. Earned Master's degree in education at Stanford. Has a young son."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-13-tmmyn",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "bullet",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-11-5k21l",
									"text": "Cami Blakely",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-12-fgjyc",
									"text": " (Boise): Now Cami Christen. Lives in Portland, Oregon. Works for Bonneville Power."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-17-svv00",
