									"text": "Melissa Bowles",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-15-x6ad8",
									"text": " (Preston): Now Melissa Bowles-Terry. Earned "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-16-8qajo",
									"text": "bachelor's and master's degrees in literature from Utah State, taught freshman and sophomore composition. Married a fellow grad student in English in 2007. Moved to Illinois, got a master's degree in library and information science, then moved to Laramie, Wyoming to work at University of Wyoming libraries. Has a young daughter."
								}
							]
						},
