							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-25-8316n",
									"text": "Audrey Dutton",
									"marks": [
										"strong"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-26-nzi2d",
									"text": " (Twin Falls): Went to Hamline University (in St. Paul, Minnesota), stayed in Minnesota for a couple years, working at a mental health clinic and f"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-27-22w6z",
									"text": "reelancing for an alt-weekly. Went to journalism school at Columbia in New York. W"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-28-hjbwe",
									"text": "orked at various newspapers in D.C. Came home to Idaho in 2011, currently a business reporter for the Idaho Statesman. Write about health care a lot, gets to tell people's stories. Loves it. Now lives with long-time boyfriend & two kittens."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-31-3gx51",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "bullet",
							"level": 1,
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-30-0sr09",
									"text": "Afton-Dawn Ellison (Boise): Now Afton-Dawn Johnson. Attended BYU. Married with two daughters. Lives in Brussels, Belgium."
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-34-um3lv",
							"style": "normal",
							"listItem": "bullet",
