								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-83-0c98q",
									"text": "Danielle McClenahan (Boise): Lives in Tacoma, WA. Works as the purchasing manager for a company that does organic produce home delivery. Recently married. She and her husband own a home, love gardening, landscaping, and camping."
