								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-95-shzfi",
									"text": " (Cascade): Graduated high school and went to the University of Idaho (degree in Industrial and Organizational Psychology). Moved to Boise, Idaho and founded a tech company called BookLamp, which specializes in using computers to analyze writing (sort of a Pandora.com for books). Latest project is called "
