							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-140-9yopt",
									"text": " Bev Buretta (Laurel's childhood next door neighbor and 'second mother') signs the guest book.[/caption]\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-141-e5xcv",
									"text": "In terms of seating, we had just under 100 total guests, seated at 13 circular tables (with 6-8 guests per table).\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-142-xlwnb",
									"text": "[caption id=\"attachment_847\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"500\"]"
								}
