								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-88-l4xnb",
									"href": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7YX0cpmcZqw"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-91-mo6an",
									"href": "http://whiskeyclone.net/hijacked/concertinfo.php?concertID=455&searchResults=414,413,415,416,417,418,419,640,420,421,422,423,783,424,425,426,427,428,429,718,430,431,432,683,433,434,435,436,437,438,788,439,440,441,442,443,444,445,446,447,448,449,450,630,451,685,452,453,454,455,456,457,458,459,460,461,462,463,464,465,466,467,468,469,470,471,472,473,474,475,476,477,478,479,480,481,482,483,484,485,486,487,488,489,490,491,492,493,494,495,496,497,498,499,500,501,502,503,504,505,506,507,508,509,510,511,512"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-95-oyi8n",
									"href": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/neil-strauss-sexx-laws.jpg"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-97-e9jgj",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/neil-strauss-sexx-laws.jpg?w=300",
								"url": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/neil-strauss-sexx-laws.jpg?w=300"
							},
							"alt": "Still from the set of &quot;Sexx Laws&quot; video"
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-111-5l5dm",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-98-wxniy",
									"text": "[/caption]\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-99-odkue",
									"text": "So this post is finally getting to the time of my life that I wanted to write about when I first embarked on detailing my abiding love for Beck, namely the masterpiece that is "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-101-ddxft",
									"text": "Midnite Vultures",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-100-5d8jc"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-102-avfym",
									"text": ". As a freshman at BYU, my closest friends were my roommate Spencer, and the two guys who lived in the dorm room next to us, Mark and Jordan. Jordan was a guitar performance major and a tech/noise/sound wizard, Mark had been the lead singer in a rock band in high school that pretty much defined his identity, and Spencer was a sneaky good guitarist/songwriter. So I was surrounded by music and we were always sharing music and weird things we found on the internet. Mark spent probably the equivalent of two months watching U2 videos, air drumming, and kicking in doors with his Bono-inspired enthusiasm, Jordan beat Tony Hawk Pro Skater 2 probably 50 times and recorded a whole album of experimental dance music with a little USB turntable thing his uncle sent him (here's a sample track), and Spencer just kept changing my wallpaper to animal-on-animal humping pictures. My contribution was staying up until 3 in the morning winning a title on NBA 2000 with teams like the Bucks and sharing Beck videos. They were all awesome, but the greatest Beck video, and quite possibly the greatest music video of all time was "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-104-e4hcw",
									"text": "the extended version of Sexx Laws",
									"marks": [
										"key-103-1mwr4"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-105-mzrsq",
									"text": " (if you want to download the file, it's "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-107-0cmwk",
									"text": "here",
									"marks": [
										"key-106-szwoi"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-108-mcjjo",
									"text": "). We probably watched this video a thousand times--all of us had the whole Vision Warrior's men's power group dialogue memorized, and it was the source of inexhaustible laughter.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-109-507jy",
									"text": "[caption id=\"attachment_111\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"300\" caption=\"Neil Strauss, lady-seductifier.\"]"
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-100-5d8jc",
									"href": "http://grooveshark.com/#/album/Midnite+Vultures/2545127?src=5"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-103-1mwr4",
									"href": "http://www.dailymotion.com/video/x4gkl9_beck-sexx-laws-long-version_music"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-106-szwoi",
									"href": "/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Beck_Sexx_Laws_Long_Version.flv"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-110-y4oag",
									"href": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/neil-strauss.jpg"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"_type": "image",
							"_key": "key-112-b9yyb",
							"asset": {
								"_type": "reference",
								"_ref": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/neil-strauss.jpg?w=300",
								"url": "http://steelwagstaff.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/neil-strauss.jpg?w=300"
							},
							"alt": "Photo of Neil Strauss, straight playa"
						},
						{
							"_type": "block",
							"_key": "key-136-qej38",
							"style": "normal",
							"children": [
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-113-l60bm",
									"text": "[/caption]\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-114-zjjrz",
									"text": "The video itself is a gem and seems like the kind of thing that would have been super fun to make, with the cast featuring a young Jack Black (this was before "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-115-scnug",
									"text": "High Fidelity ",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-116-1b20m",
									"text": "you have to remember, at a time when we was making things like "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-118-3x2td",
									"text": "Heat",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-117-uokqt"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-119-4rrm9",
									"text": " ",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-121-8k5c4",
									"text": "Vision",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-120-m9333"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-122-lh7yo",
									"text": " ",
									"marks": [
										"em"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-124-3bkp9",
									"text": "and Jack",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-123-w1vc3"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-125-6g8ct",
									"text": ") talking about his glorious washerboard abs and his dolphin fetish (while wearing a beeeeea-uuu-tiful t-shirt), "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-127-wyapn",
									"text": "Justin Meldal-Johnsen",
									"marks": [
										"key-126-vb771"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-128-e4u41",
									"text": ", Beck's then bassist, talking about his belief that his spirit was so large it just might be able to plug up the hole in the ozone layer, and Neil Strauss, the journalist who gained a measure of infamy after reinventing himself as a pick-up artist while participating in and writing about the seduction community in the "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-130-r7jnv",
									"text": "NYT",
									"marks": [
										"key-129-o5ig7"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-131-v668f",
									"text": " and his best-selling "
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-133-4cbbp",
									"text": "The Game: Penetrating the Secret Society of Pickup Artists",
									"marks": [
										"em",
										"key-132-wb9ek"
									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-134-r2w49",
									"text": ", appearing as a decidedly unsexy angel lover who wants \"angel answers\" and who yearns to write a book about angels and then give it away. In short, it is impossibly funny, incredibly strange, and really really good.\n\n"
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "key-135-g4kcy",
									"text": "And before you go, I just want you to remember one thing: I know what you are. ... You're a ficus."
								}
							],
							"markDefs": [
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-117-uokqt",
									"href": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WHvjcsELcjA"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-120-m9333",
									"href": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YE0PtCh2AyM"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-123-w1vc3",
									"href": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dDGA8PgivNI"
								},
								{
									"_type": "link",
									"_key": "key-126-vb771",
									"href": "http://www.justinmj.com/"
								},
								{
