									]
								},
								{
									"_type": "span",
									"_key": "k6",
									"text": "\" We took a look at ROY songs, songs whose titles corresponded to the warm end of that spectrum [Red, Orange, & Yellow]. The recording equipment in the studio wasn't working this week. Sorry. You can listen to the Spotify playlist below, however, to hear most of what we played this week.",
